title: Indonesia 30 Year bond-Yield
description: Indonesia 30 Year Bond Yield was 7.56 percent on Tuesday November 8, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Indonesia 30 Year bond-Yield reached an all time high of 21.67 in October of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for Indonesia 30Y.
